membership:
CIVILSCAPE closely co-operates with UNISCAPE, the network of universities and research institutes for landscape research.&#xd;
&#xd;
CIVILSCAPE is member of the European Heritage Alliance and contributes to the network activities.&#xd;
&#xd;
CIVILSCAPE has been member of the European Year of Citizens 2013 Alliance and played an active role to involve their national and regional member organisations in the national coalitions.&#xd;
&#xd;
CIVILSCAPE has also signed the Rennewable Grid Declaration and promotes these ideas, concepts and best-practice example from different countries. &#xd;
&#xd;
CIVILSCAPE is member of the ARC2020 network and supports their work with contributions on local, regional and national level.

